      "created_at": "2023-08-15T09:55:43.174Z",
      "cooked": "<p>It\u2019s interesting.  I really like dynamic training, I like ERG for a lot of indoor training but I think it should be used in a more dynamic way.  So what you are suggesting supports that.  The problem is we are small so we need to prioritize things based on what seems that will benefit a larger audience.  As this gets more popular or we get bigger it seems more possible.</p>",
